OL,3,C'World's largest' vacuum used to suck
OL,4,Cpollution out of the air begins
OL,5,Coperation
OL,7,FThe "world's largest" plant designed
OL,8,Fto suck planet-heating pollution out
OL,9,Fof the atmosphere began operating in
OL,10,FIceland on Wednesday.
OL,12,F"Mammoth" will work like a giant
OL,13,Fvacuum to suck in air and strip out
OL,14,Fthe carbon using chemicals. The carbon
OL,15,Fcan then be injected deep beneath the
OL,16,Fground, reused, or transformed into
OL,17,Fsolid products.
