OL,3,C'World's largest' vacuum used to suck
OL,4,Cpollution out of the air begins
OL,5,Coperation
OL,7,FThe technology is called Direct air
OL,8,Fcapture, or DAC. Mammoth is the second
OL,9,FDAC plant operated by Swiss company
OL,10,FClimeworks and is ten times bigger
OL,11,Fthan its predecessor, Orca, which
OL,12,Fstarted running in 2021.
OL,14,FClimeworks plans to transport the
OL,15,Funderground where it will be naturally
OL,16,Ftransformed into stone, meaning the
OL,17,Fcarbon will be locked up forever.
OL,19,FThe operation will be powered by
OL,20,FIceland's abundant geothermal energy.
