OL,5,Coperation
OL,7,FMammoth will pull up to 36,000 tons of
OL,8,Fcarbon from the atmosphere a year.
OL,9,FThat's equivalent to taking about
OL,10,F7,800 gas-powered cars off the road.
OL,12,FScientists say the world needs to find
OL,13,Fways to remove carbon from the
OL,14,Fatmosphere, in order to mitigate the
OL,15,Feffects of .
OL,17,FAnd as the planet solutions such as
OL,18,FDAC are gaining more attention from
OL,19,Fgovernments and private companies.
