OL,7,FBut the technology is still
OL,8,Fcontroversial, having been criticised
OL,9,Fas expensive, energy-hungry, and
OL,10,Funproven at scale.
OL,12,FCarbon capture in general is "fraught
OL,13,Fwith uncertainties and ecological
OL,14,Frisks", according to Lili Fuhr of the
OL,15,FCentre for International Environment
OL,16,Flaw.
