OL,7,FAll the in the world is only capable
OL,8,Fof removing around 0.01 million metric
OL,9,Ftons of carbon a year - a far cry from
OL,10,Fthe 70 million tons a year needed by
OL,11,F2030 to meet global climate goals.
OL,13,FBut Climeworks says they have
OL,14,Fambitions to increase their scale of
OL,15,Fcarbon removal by building new plants
OL,16,Fin the next six years.
